  "text": "Northern Blot Analysis. Northern blot analysis ofmRNAs from CBl cells and a positive control was carried out using a specific MYCMHZ probe previously described [CITATION_1] . The myCMH2 3' probe was derived from a chicken genomic library and it represents the 3' region of the avian myc gene which does not crosshybridize with the murine myc genes.",
